Data* (star) Observatory is the fancy website you are currently viewing.

Its goal: to help [software architects](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_architect) quickly catch up with latest [DB-related](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Database) tech.

The navigable main visually maps software (orange planets) and technical concepts (purple planets) into areas of different topics.
Clicking on such a planet will reveal a short description, list of related entities and directions for further research.

